SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-312 - Orca LNG Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-312 to Orca LNG Ltd. to export gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of the liquefaction terminal to be located on the vicinity of Prince Rupert, British Columbia.
